<div class="block" id="last_comments"><div class="title_contaner"><div class="title_contaner1"></div><div class="title_contaner2">Последние комментарии</div><div class="title_contaner3"></div></div><div class="clear"></div><div class="margin3"><div class="lastcomments">
&nbsp;<b class="lasuser">Moo3</b> пишет:<br />
